    "Scores by languages.",
    "Table 4 presents the results in legal contents by all 23 languages in EUR-LEX.",
    "We present the best performing model of Gemma2-9B in finetuned and fewshot conditions.",
    "We also present the averaged results of 10 models in Table 3 without GPTs to highlight the performance difference before and after finetuning with LegalViz across languages, while minimizing the influence of individual model characteristics.",
    "Among these languages, models perform relatively weakly in languages that have relatively fewer resources (Chalkidis et al., 2021a), such as Maltese, Latvian, Lithuanian, Hungarian."
